ana; font-size:16pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">highway</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt"> operator”?</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">Informed opinion suggests that the Highways Agency in its present form should, if anything, take</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">on</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt"> a more</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">arm's length relationship</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">with the Department of Transport when its current agreements</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">expire</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt"> in 2015.</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">That apart, NECTAR can see </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">no point in aiming to be a</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">"world leader" in a field that is essentially</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">confined</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt"> to</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">the one country which it is supposed to be working for. Or are we, perhaps, threatened</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">with</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt"> a Europe-wide open</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">market for competitive bids between the equivalent b</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">odies in other countries</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">              </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">for</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt"> the privilege/right/curse of</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:13pt">looking after main roads in any other EU member country?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt"> 6b</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">What</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt"> roles should Government and the private sector play to ensure better</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">management</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt"> of the strategic road network?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:16pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><