pan></p><p style="line-height:16pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">This conclude</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">s the responses that we as NECTAR wish to send to the committee.</span></p><p style="line-height:16pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:16pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">NECTAR is the North-East Combined Transport Activists' Roundtable, and we have contributed responses to several</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:16pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">other</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">HoC</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt"> Inquiries on transport-related matters.</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:16pt; margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">              </span></p><p style="line-height:16pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:16pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">Contact details: </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">P J W</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">alker (co-ordinator), 26 Devon Crescent, </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">Billingham</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">, </span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">Tees</span><span style="font-family:LucidaSans; font-size:14pt">-side.</span></p><p style="line-height:16pt; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt"><span styl